imdb.plot outline: ChuChu TV Funzone is a new 3D series from ChuChu TV Studios where Wanny, Spanny and Mr.Eggsie travel to the funzone in an awesome train ride and learn lot of things while playing games. We hope these colorful 3D Visuals engage your kids and provide them with new kind of entertainment.
